Embark on an Unforgettable Whitsundays Adventure!
From pristine waterfalls to the purest white sand in the world, this package has it all. Discover some of the Whitsundays best-kept secrets with Red Cat Adventures over any 3 days of your choice. This package includes 3 of our national award-winning all-inclusive day tours, Thundercat, Falls to Paradise and the Tongarra Day Sail.
The multi (2018/2019/2021) Australian GOLD award-winning tour visits the world-famous Whitehaven Beach, Hill Inlet lookout and offers 2 snorkelling opportunities on the fringing Great Barrier Reef.
Thundercat is the fastest catamaran in the Whitsundays and has been designed for stability and speed so it’s perfect for passengers who are concerned about seasickness. The all-inclusive package departs from Airlie Beach and is suitable for families, couples and groups wanting to experience once in a lifetime moments.
Thundercat is proud to be accredited as a Climate Action Leading tour. This is the highest level of ECO certification offered in Australia
Falls to Paradise is an all-inclusive day tour exploring Cedar Creek Falls where guests can swim in the rockpools at waterfalls, surrounded by tropical flora and fauna. Follow this with a chill-out session around the iconic Northerlies Beach Bar & Grill and enjoy the spectacular scenery of the Coral Sea and Whitsunday Islands. This is a great all-around day to enjoy with family and friends.
Get ready for a fun day out on the water! We’re kicking things off with an easy check-in, then cruising straight to Langford, a stunning island paradise where the sand is as white as the vibe is chill. Kick back on the spacious deck with comfy beanbags, soak up the sun, and get ready for the ultimate day of adventure!
So grab your camera, feel the ocean breeze in your hair and enjoy Whitsunday’s unique locations.
