Adventure with Australia’s BEST!
Thundercat offers the “”Adventure of a lifetime”” around the Whitsunday Islands in one day. The multiple national award-winning tour visits the world-famous Whitehaven Beach, Hill Inlet lookout, and offers 2 snorkels on the fringing Great Barrier Reef. Thundercat has been custom-built for stability and speed, perfect for travellers concerned about seasickness.
Tongarra: This sailing vessel is the perfect option for either day tours or overnight sailing tours (private charter only). Grab your favourite friends and spend the day relaxing on the deck in the sun and eating delicious food as we sail to your next destination. Filled with adventure and stunning views at the best holiday spots around the Whitsundays, plus snorkelling in the pristine waters of the Great Barrier Reef, you are sure to feel refreshed and relaxed after this epic experience. Our friendly and experienced crew will prepare you fresh meals on the BBQ and take you for a spin on our “Red Shark” banana boat to give you some extra thrills. While our boat provides sleeping quarters, you can keep the party going late into the night when you opt to sleep under the stars.
This all-inclusive day tour will take you off the beaten track to experience the Whitsunday Islands’ secret spots. You will explore the most incredible range of marine life and witness the wonders of the Great Barrier Reef from above and below the surface.
As an award-winning multinational business and accredited Climate Action Leaders, we invite you to relax with your friends or family. Tongarra day sail offers a large comfortable deck, spacious seating, chilled tunes and spectacular scenery. We provide informative history talks, and guests will learn from our experienced crew about the reefs and the beautiful islands. Snorkel at pristine locations in secluded anchorages and bays and come face to face with tropical fish, colourful corals and more.
