Experience the beauty of the world-famous Great Barrier Reef on this snorkelling eco-adventure. Travel on the smoothest, most comfortable vessel to visit the incredible coral wonderland of the outer reefs. Snorkel at the world-famous Great Barrier Reef during the day, then sit back and relax with a delicious locally catered lunch while taking in the sights and sounds of the natural world from the top deck.
The all-inclusive day trip is great for those who want to bond while reconnecting with nature, couples searching for a romantic escape, or small groups seeking adventure and fun. This once-in-a-lifetime experience will deliver unbeatable memories that will last a lifetime.
